<typeStatus box="[446,552,613,637]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">lectotype</typeStatus>
. Subsequently the second specimen becomes a 
<typeStatus box="[1090,1245,613,637]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">paralectotype</typeStatus>
. The 
<typeStatus box="[1307,1409,613,637]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">lectotype</typeStatus>
is used to illustrate the species in the figures 
<number box="[627,668,649,673]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" value="118.0">118</number>
and 
<number box="[722,766,649,673]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" value="119.0">119</number>
.
</paragraph>
